Photo by Monica 🖤 on June 28, 2021. May be an image of text that says 'global_grassroots The 2026 PG @romelo actually surprised me at @neoyouthelite camp. This is one of the biggest camps in the country with all the cameras pointing at him and he handled himself like he's been here before. He showed quickness on both sides of the ball, his IQ was present in the sense that he never tried to do too much. He understood his capabilities and stuck to the script. He guarded, he handled pressure and he showed he can hoop with some of the best.| was impressed young man, keep going @neoyouthelite @rikki_by_ricky'.
